      "title": "33,000 liters of fuel was wasted on the road",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Bowser carrying fuel from Trincomalee IOC fuel depot to Haputhala fuel depot met with an accident.",
        "This morning, while carrying 33000 liters of fuel, the Bowser met with an accident in Haputhalai- Panketiya area.",
        "It is reported that the accident occurred due to slippery road and no one was injured."
